from `_Message` and the stored object of type [error_code](../standard-library/error-code-class.md) (either `code` or `error_code(_Errval, _Errcat)`).  \n  \n The member function `code` returns the stored [error_code](../standard-library/error-code-class.md) object.  \n  \n## Requirements  \n **Header:** <system_error>  \n  \n **Namespace:** std  \n  \n## See Also  \n [<system_error>](../standard-library/system-error.md)\n\n"}